00:15:10.480 --> 00:15:14.510
challenges of working on
a distributed display.

00:15:14.510 --> 00:15:16.930
It does work on a
single machine.

00:15:16.930 --> 00:15:22.030
And I don't foresee a lot of
integration and refactoring

00:15:22.030 --> 00:15:26.430
effort required to get this all
working within a single

00:15:26.430 --> 00:15:27.900
